                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How long have you know the prisoner? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Several years—I thought him a respectable man—I never had any bill transaction with him.</p>
